= subs( IC, NEWTON_EQ_S );" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6#>%,NEWTO
N_EQ_SG/*(&%\"JG6#%$eq1G\"\"\")%\"sG\"\"#\"\"\"&%&ThetaG6#\"\"\"\"\"\"
